'''perioscope'''


== English ==



=== Noun ===


perioscope, ''plural'' perioscopes

1. A dental diagnostic instrument consisting of a tiny camera and a display screen.  The camera can be inserted between gums and teeth to display a highly magnified image of the area.  This simplifies finding and removing plaque and tartar.

2. The diagnostic procedure using a perioscope


=== Verb ===


1. to examine with a perioscope